{
  "text": "City branding has been defined as the \"purposeful symbolic embodiment of all information connected to a city in order to create associations around it\" [CITATION_1] . It can be used as a strategic tool to provide cities with a source of economic, political, and cultural value [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . It can also be seen as an instrument to communicate the city's competitive advantage, the quality of the place, its history, lifestyle, and culture [CITATION_4] . There is a growing body of research and practice related to city branding [CITATION_5] .",
